  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the ttukbaegi earthenware pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the olive oil and saute the chopped onion until translucent.",
    "Add the grated carrot and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the brown rice and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Fluff the rice with a fork and stir in the crumbled fiordilatte cheese.",
    "Add the canned tuna, ttukbaegi earthenware pot seasoning, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
